Exeggutor (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0102: Exeggcute
Pokémon
#0104: Cubone →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Exeggutor (TCG Pocket).

Exeggutor has been featured on 33 different cards since it debuted in the Jungle expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Exeggutor cards are normally Grass-type, Psychic-type, or Dragon-type Stage 1 Pokémon. As a Dragon-type, their attacks normally have costs including and Energy.
